item.title: Paul contributions
item.dc:creator: @paul
item.description:
@paul wrote:

euxo/in/led-button.axo

status

ready to use.

description:

4 inputs to trigger LEDs on/off.
* GPIOC,0 = LED 1
* GPIOC,2 = LED 2
* GPIOC,4 = LED 3
* GPIOA,0 = LED 4

4 outputs for one of the pushbutton.
GPIOC,1 = Button 1
GPIOC,3 = Button 2
GPIOC,5 = Button 3
GPIOA,1 = Button 4
